{"lemma":"نَثْرُ","slug":"نَثْرُ","root":"ن.ث.ر","root_slug":"ن-ث-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ث-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39316","","n39319","n39320","n39321"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AB%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to disperse, to dissipate, to scatter, to sprinkle, to ruffle, to fling"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to disperse, to dissipate, to scatter"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of نَثَرَ (naṯara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"prose"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/na.θa.ra/","/naθ.θa.ra/","/naθr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39316","headword_ar":"نَثَرَ","root":"nvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navorN","text_ar":"نَثْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nivaArN","text_ar":"نِثَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) or the latter is a simple subst., (S, A, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He scattered"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprinkled"},{"kind":"text","text":"it,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strewed"},{"kind":"text","text":"it,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersed"},{"kind":"text","text":"it, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"threw"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dispersedly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, M, A, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with his hand;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T;) as, for instance, grain, (Lth, T,) and fruit and the like, (Msb,) walnuts and almonds and sugar, (Lth, T,) and pearls, &c.; (A;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nv~r","text_ar":"نثّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanoviyrN","text_ar":"تَنْثِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) [or the latter is with teshdeed to denote muchness, or frequency, or repetition, of the action; or its application to many objects: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manovuwrN","text_ar":"مَنْثُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navarati Aln~axolapu","text_ar":"نَثَرَتِ النَّخْلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The palm-tree"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scattered"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shook off its unripe dates."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajaA^ahu fanavara A^amoEaA='ahu","text_ar":"وَجَاَهُ فَنَثَرَ اَمْعَا=ءَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He smote him with a knife and scattered his intestines"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, A.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA^anovuran~aka navora Alkari$i","text_ar":"لَاَنْثُرَنَّكَ نَثْرَ الكَرِشِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will assuredly scatter thine intestines like as one scatters the contents of the stomach of a ruminant beast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: said in threatening. (A.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara waladFA","text_ar":"نَثَرَ وَلَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, M)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had many children born to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navarati AlmaroA^apu baTonahaA","text_ar":"نَثَرَتِ المَرْاَةُ بَطْنَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, A, Mgh TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aA baTonihaA","text_ar":"ذَا بَطْنِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Mgh, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kari$ahaA","text_ar":"كَرِشَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kr$","text_ar":"كرش"},{"kind":"text","text":",) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The woman brought forth many children;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kr$","text_ar":"كرش"},{"kind":"text","text":";)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scattered children;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"llz~awoji","text_ar":"للزَّوْجِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the husband."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"natara AlkalaAma","text_ar":"نَتَرَ الكَلَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spoke,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"talked, much."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara qiraA'atahu","text_ar":"نَثَرَ قِرَاءَتَهُ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2763},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He hastened,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was quick, in his reading,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reciting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara","text_ar":"نَثَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naviyrN","text_ar":"نَثِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a beast of carriage, M, K, and a camel, M, and an ass, T)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sneezed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to scatter the moisture in his nostrils"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T, M, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did with his nose what is like sneezing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an ass, and a sheep or goat)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sneezed, and expelled what annoyed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt him, from his nose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navarato","text_ar":"نَثَرَتْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a ewe or goat)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ejected from her nose what annoyed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt her."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara","text_ar":"نَثَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, T, IAth, Mgh, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, IAth,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navorN","text_ar":"نَثْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Mgh) [and app."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naviyrN","text_ar":"نَثِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as above], (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a man]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blew his nose; ejected the mucus from his nose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AmotaxaTa","text_ar":"امْتَخَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAth;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mxT","text_ar":"مخط"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he ejected what was in his nose, of mucus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of that which annoyed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurt him, in performing the ablution termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuDuwo'","text_ar":"وُضُوْء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Sgh, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anovara","text_ar":"اَنْثَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to some: (TA:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anovara","text_ar":"اَنْثَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he ejected what was in his nose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he emitted his breath from his nose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he introduced the water into his nose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Antvr","text_ar":"انتثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) but this last explanation is outweighed in authority; the form ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Anvr","text_ar":"انثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is disallowed by the leading lexicologists; and the author of the K, in respect of this form, follows Sgh, without due consideration: (TA:) [accord. to the more approved opinion,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara","text_ar":"نَثَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he scattered what was in his nose by the breath;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Antvr","text_ar":"انتثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or, as some of the learned say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he snuffed up water, and then ejected what was in it, of anything annoying"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hurting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of mucus;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAar, T, Mgh:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, IAth, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Antvr","text_ar":"انتثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he snuffed up water, and then ejected it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, IAth, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the breath of the nose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, K:) accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara","text_ar":"نَثَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a person performing"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuDuwo'","text_ar":"وُضُوْء"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"snuffed up water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but others say that the latter signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he ejected what was in his nose, of mucus &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"agreeably with a trad. to be cited below: (Msb:) IAar says, that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he snuffed up water, and put in motion the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navorap","text_ar":"نَثْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"end of the nose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in purification: (T [in the Mgh, this explanation is ascribed to Fr:]) and Fr, that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara","text_ar":"نَثَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Antvr","text_ar":"انتثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put in motion the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navorap","text_ar":"نَثْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", in purification. (T.) It is said of Mohammad,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna yasotano$iqu valaAvFA","text_ar":"كَانَ يَسْتَنْشِقُ ثَلَاثًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY kul~i mar~apK yasotanoviru","text_ar":"فِى كُلِّ مَرَّةٍ يَسْتَنْثِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He used to snuff up water three times, every time ejecting it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] and this indicates that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"differs from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astn$q","text_ar":"استنشق"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, Mgh, Msb.) And it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA","text_ar":"اـِذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@sotano$aqota faA@novuro","text_ar":"ا@سْتَنْشَقْتَ فَا@نْثُرْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA@noviro","text_ar":"فَا@نْثِرْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the conjunctive"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":", and with damm and kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"v","text_ar":"ث"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"When thou snuffest up water, scatter what is in thy nose by the breath;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eject what is in thy nose, of mucus, &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or, as A'Obeyd relates it, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^anoviro","text_ar":"فَاَنْثِرْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inovaArN","text_ar":"اـِنْثَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) or, as he relates it"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*aA tawaD~aAta faA^anoviro","text_ar":"اـِذَا تَوَضَّاتَ فَاَنْثِرْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the disjunctive"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and he does not explain it; but the lexicologists do not allow ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anovara","text_ar":"اَنْثَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_inovaAru","text_ar":"الاـِنْثَارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; one only says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara","text_ar":"نَثَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Antvr","text_ar":"انتثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) No instance of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astnvr","text_ar":"استنثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"used transitively has been heard, except in a trad. of El-Hasan Ibn-'Alee,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofahu","text_ar":"اَنْفَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotanovara","text_ar":"اِسْتَنْثَرَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ejected the contents of his nose;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he blew his nose"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as though the root ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navara","text_ar":"نَثَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] were regarded in it, or as though it were made to import the meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naq~aY","text_ar":"نَقَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","A","Msb","K","Lth","T","TA","Mgh","Fr","IAth","IAar"]},{"entry_id":"n39319","headword_ar":"نَثْرٌ","root":"nvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Prose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so accord. to general usage: and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rhyming prose: contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naZomN","text_ar":"نَظْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so called as being likened to [scattered pearls, or] scattered grain. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n39320","headword_ar":"نَثَرٌ","root":"nvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuvaArN","text_ar":"نُثَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nivaArN","text_ar":"نِثَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munotavirN","text_ar":"مُنْتَثِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Loquacity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"divulging of secrets."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n39321","headword_ar":"نَثِرٌ","root":"nvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Loquacious;"},{"kind":"text","text":"one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who talks much:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"minovarN","text_ar":"مِنْثَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nayovuraAnN","text_ar":"نَيْثُرَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Sgh, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vainly"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frivolously loquacious, and a divulger of secrets:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"navirapN","text_ar":"نَثِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"only. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","Sgh","A"]}]}}